Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:36.66,OP ROMANJI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Kok suruh, mambutah, main'o, densha noh nakal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:43.76,OP ROMANJI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Mari ngentit ndek kono, ijin'no extra mie tai
